# ServiceFlow CRM Project Overview

This is a Next.js based CRM application for service businesses. It's built with TypeScript, uses Supabase for backend services, and Tailwind CSS for styling.

## Key Files and Directories

- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Main layout component for the Next.js application
- [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Homepage component
- [middleware.ts](mdc:middleware.ts) - Middleware for authentication and routing
- [src/lib/supabase](mdc:src/lib/supabase) - Supabase client configuration

## Application Structure

- `src/app` - Next.js app router pages and API routes
- `src/components` - Reusable UI components
- `src/lib` - Utility functions and service configurations
- `src/hooks` - Custom React hooks
- `src/context` - React context providers
- `src/types` - TypeScript type definitions

